The Aroma-Snooze Sleep Aid and Organic Oils have created a massive positive difference in your child's ability to get to sleep quicker and stay asleep longer too! 

This revolutionary 6 in 1 Sleep Aid has everything you wanted all in the one device! 
🙏 Red Light therapy to support melatonin naturally
🙏 5 built in music tracks, including pink noise and lullabys
🙏 Built in voice recorder to record your own Shusshing sound, 
🙏 Organic Oil to help relax and settle
🙏 Advanced ultrasonic technology to help purify the air
🙏 Gently humidifiers the air for improved breathing and comfort

@love.alice.x  shows how easy the Aroma-snooze is to set up and use, and 20 month old Alice loves her new night time routine! ❤❤❤
#3littlecrowns #aromasnooze #babydiffuser
